item.description: Deliver high quality Lambda functions Dashbird works by collecting logs through your AWS Cloudwatch API. How it works? Quickly find and fix production errors Tracking and alerting errors from all your Lambda functions. Stacktraces and context helps you troubleshoot errors quickly and easily. Get closer to your code while developing it Real time insights after each deploy. Execution data and logs let you iterate quicky after deploys.
